            <p>The Fort Frances Sportsmen's Club is run by members for members. As such, the club’s survival as well as the quality of the membership experience 
                offered to all members is dependent on club members getting involved in organizing or helping to organize events, 
                and assisting with the management of the club’s business affairs and meetings, in addition to participating in activities offered by the club.</p>

            <p>One year membership in the Fort Frances Sportmen's Club includes:</p>
                <ul>
